items.name: case invalid
items.desc: The session is in an invalid or uninitialized state.

items.name: case waiting
items.desc: The session is waiting for better conditions before attempting to make the session ready.

items.name: case preparing
items.desc: The remote endpoint is being resolved.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: The session is ready for reading and writing data.

items.name: case failed
items.desc: None of the currently resolved endpoints can be used at this time, either due to problems with the path or the client rejecting the endpoints.

items.name: case cancelled
items.desc: The session has been cancelled by the client calling cancel.
